    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1525059/" class="title-link">价格很贵呀</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1525059"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/song1960/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1805066-25.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/song1960/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">宋歪麦</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-10-15"
      class="main-meta">2008-10-15 03:18:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1525059_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   作者知识量不小，却试图在一本书里炫耀，很牵强。写的一般，试图包罗万象，作为导论不需深入，但也要让人入门，但读者没能入半个门，作者就跳到另一题目了。    翻译和原著比，更差一档次。看不出是顾肃的作品，的确有损顾肃名声。  强烈不推荐

